---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Nico Grassetto" description="Learn more about Nico Grassetto">	<section class="about-section">
		<h2>About Nico Grassetto</h2>
		
		<div class="bio-content">
			<p class="intro">
				Nico Grassetto is a passionate web developer and technology enthusiast dedicated to crafting thoughtful digital experiences using cutting-edge technologies.
			</p>
			
			<h3>Professional Journey</h3>
			<p>
				With expertise spanning JavaScript, TypeScript, React, and various modern frontend frameworks, Nico has built a career around creating intuitive and performant web applications. His approach combines technical precision with user-centered design principles, ensuring that every project delivers both functionality and exceptional user experience.
			</p>
			
			<h3>Technical Expertise</h3>
			<ul class="skills-list">
				<li><strong>Frontend Technologies:</strong> JavaScript, TypeScript, React, Astro.js, HTML5, CSS3</li>
				<li><strong>Backend & Cloud:</strong> Node.js, Azure, Modern deployment strategies</li>
				<li><strong>Development Tools:</strong> Git, VS Code, Modern build tools and workflows</li>
				<li><strong>Specializations:</strong> Performance optimization, responsive design, accessibility</li>
			</ul>
			
			<h3>Philosophy & Approach</h3>
			<p>
				Nico believes in the power of continuous learning and staying current with the rapidly evolving web development landscape. He actively contributes to open source projects and enjoys sharing knowledge through his blog, covering topics ranging from practical development techniques to emerging technologies and industry best practices.
			</p>
			
			<p>
				When not coding, Nico can be found exploring new web technologies, contributing to the developer community, or working on personal projects that push the boundaries of what's possible on the web.
			</p>
			
			<div class="cta">
				<p>Interested in collaborating or learning more about my work? Feel free to reach out through the blog or connect on professional networks.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>

<style>
.about-section {
	padding: 2rem;
	max-width: 700px;
	margin: 0 auto;
}

.about-section h2 {
	font-size: 2rem;
	margin-bottom: 2rem;
	text-align: center;
	color: var(--text-primary);
}

.bio-content {
	text-align: left;
}

.intro {
	font-size: 1.125rem;
	line-height: 1.7;
	margin-bottom: 2rem;
	color: var(--text-secondary);
	font-style: italic;
	text-align: center;
	padding: 1rem;
	border-left: 3px solid var(--border-primary);
	background: var(--bg-secondary);
	border-radius: 4px;
}

.bio-content h3 {
	font-size: 1.25rem;
	font-weight: 600;
	margin: 2rem 0 1rem 0;
	color: var(--text-primary);
	border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-primary);
	padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
}

.bio-content p {
	font-size: 1rem;
	line-height: 1.6;
	margin-bottom: 1rem;
	color: var(--text-secondary);
}

.skills-list {
	list-style: none;
	padding: 0;
	margin: 1rem 0 2rem 0;
}

.skills-list li {
	padding: 0.5rem 0;
	border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-primary);
	color: var(--text-secondary);
}

.skills-list li:last-child {
	border-bottom: none;
}

.skills-list strong {
	color: var(--text-primary);
	font-weight: 600;
}

.cta {
	margin-top: 2rem;
	padding: 1.5rem;
	background: var(--bg-secondary);
	border-radius: 8px;
	border: 1px solid var(--border-primary);
	text-align: center;
}

.cta p {
	margin: 0;
	font-size: 1rem;
	color: var(--text-secondary);
	font-style: italic;
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
	.about-section {
		padding: 1.5rem;
	}
	
	.about-section h2 {
		font-size: 1.75rem;
	}
	
	.intro {
		font-size: 1rem;
		padding: 0.75rem;
	}
	
	.bio-content h3 {
		font-size: 1.125rem;
	}
}
</style>
